00:40:59.760 --> 00:41:01.270
knowledgeable about something.

00:41:01.270 --> 00:41:03.050
Does anybody know who this is?

00:41:07.090 --> 00:41:08.162
Oh, all right.

00:41:08.162 --> 00:41:09.745
Well, let me see if
